        <h2>Depression Goggles</h2>
        <p>
            Often when you're struggling with depression, you're the last person to recognize it.  Depression goggles is the
            way that our brains trick themselves into believing that the dark way we look at the world when we're struggling
            is the way that we always look at the world.  Conversely, our better days also appear to be the way we always
            feel, from the inside.
        </p>
